Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.generic_scpi.SCPIMultimeter, ['SAMP:COUN?',
    'SAMP:COUN?', 'SAMP:COUN MIN', 'SAMP:COUN 10'], ['+10', 'MAX']) as dmm:
    assert dmm.sample_count == 10
    assert dmm.sample_count == dmm.SampleCount.maximum
    dmm.sample_count = dmm.SampleCount.minimum
    dmm.sample_count = 10
